WEBVTT

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:31.320
they can have to go back in as short
as just a few days after giving birth.

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:35.736
How do we optimize
mother and infant health

00:07:35.760 --> 00:07:39.096
just by messaging
about breast milk to moms

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:41.896
without providing
the institutional support

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:44.576
that facilitates
that mother-infant bonding

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:46.040
to support breastfeeding?

00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:48.680
The answer is: we can't.

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:53.456
I'm talking to you, legislators,

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:55.416
and the voters who elect them.

00:07:55.440 --> 00:08:00.136
I'm talking to you, job creators
and collective bargaining units,